# UI Components Rules

## Core Screens
- Main Screen: Navigation and transitions
- Character Creation: Profession and stats
- Game Map: AR view and markers
- Combat: Health bars and actions
- Inventory: Items and equipment

## Common Components
- Health/Mana Bars
- Action Buttons
- Status Cards
- Scrollable Lists

## Styling
- Use StyleSheet.create
- Consistent theme
- Mobile-first approach
- Proper spacing

## Accessibility
- Readable text
- Touch targets
- Clear feedback
- Error states
